{"tid":1286974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[勝利要訣]提防保皇 小心打手","createTime":"2019-07-05T04:35:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T08:58:40.000Z","uid":38523,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4e5d9cb37b4aafa5c7d6c5b3796a51f7fd00c565","tid":1286974,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:35:02.000Z","msg":"大家要小心保皇狗打手借頭借路去攻擊同我地同路既政黨<br />\n開始用自已既幻想既將來<br />\n潛移默化咁透過攻擊政敵<br />\n將保皇狗既劣勢慢慢拉回<br />\n佢地做既只需要不停攻擊泛民<br />\n講到自己出謀獻計咁<br />\n實際上係為他日分化而鋪路<br />\n之後結合標題黨 假消息等攻擊保皇狗政敵<br />\n但求係下次穩住席位<br />\n再推多次條例<br />\n記住分化手段有好多<br />\n而保皇狗打手最擅長既就係<br />\n扮晒為香港好咁攻擊政敵<br />\n如果唔係保皇狗控制大多數議席<br />\n根本唔洗有義士出來冒險<br />\n家小心保皇狗分化既計劃"},{"pid":"897e1ccc753dbcfabbccc791b883fd32dde369c2","tid":1286974,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:37:37.000Z","msg":"。。。。"},{"pid":"deda2cea3962a29686ce94ddb2e1f1f9505528c2","tid":1286974,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:42:03.000Z","msg":"。。。。"},{"pid":"7a19ce3d10bacd9b58b97042ed1351e1056d61b4","tid":1286974,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:47:04.000Z","msg":"。。。。"},{"pid":"3154c4bbdab0d8df8d754c0d387133af28d0fff2","tid":1286974,"uid":261627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:47:45.000Z","msg":"不分化不割蓆"},{"pid":"3f7f54099791ad58174e2bd3655468ae0fc39f24","tid":1286974,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:58:40.000Z","msg":"。。。"}]}